AB  - We are very grateful to everyone for their support of the Review of Finance (RF) in the past, through submitting, reviewing, or reading papers, being a personal or institutional subscriber, and informing others about the journal. We are pleased to have been added to the Financial Times 50 list, but this is only a start. Our goal is to be seen as an A journal, because we believe that our ever-expanding finance profession needs more than three A journals. We know that it will take a huge amount of effort to achieve this goal, but have made many changes to try to do so. We appreciate the opportunity to communicate these changes to our readers.
Y2  - 3/26/2024
